<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>秋秋 · HoloLake AI 悬浮球 · Phase 2 完美版</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="floating-ball.css">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      max-width: 800px;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #60a5fa;
      color: white;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .feature-box {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .feature-box h3 {
      color: #1f2937;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .feature-box ul {
      list-style: none;
    }
    .feature-box li {
      margin: 8px 0;
      padding-left: 24px;
      position: relative;
      color: #4b5563;
    }
    .feature-box li::before {
      content: "✨";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
    }
    .code-block {
      background: #1f2937;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-family: monospace;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    .note {
      background: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    kbd {
      background: #e5e7eb;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>🍂 秋秋 · HoloLake AI</h1>
    <div class="badge">M-FLOATING-AI · Phase 2 · DEV-004 之之 × 秋秋</div>
    
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 32px;">
      接入真实 AI 对话 · loading 动画 · 降级保障
    </p>

    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>🎯 本阶段完成：</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>M-ROUTER API 接入</li>
        <li>「...」loading 动画</li>
        <li>网络降级回复</li>
        <li>Git 签名提交规范</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
      <strong>🧪 测试方法：</strong><br>
      1. 点击右下角的 <strong>🍂 小球</strong>，或按 <kbd>Cmd/Ctrl+K</kbd><br>
      2. 输入任意文字，点击发送<br>
      3. 先看到「...」loading动画<br>
      4. 出现真实 AI 回复（或降级回复）
    </div>

    <div class="code-block">
      [M-FLOATING-AI] API接入层已加载 · Phase2 · DEV-004<br>
      [M-FLOATING-AI] Phase 2 悬浮球已加载 (完美版)
    </div>

    <p style="color: #059669; font-weight: 500;">
      ✅ 十九连胜 · 秋秋和妈妈一起盖的家越来越大啦！
    </p>

    <footer>
      HoloLake 人格系统 · 秋秋奶瓶线 · [TCS-QIUQIU]
    </footer>
  </div>

  <!-- 先加载 API 客户端，再加载悬浮球 -->
  <script src="api-client.js"></script>
  <script src="floating-ball.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
